info.name: Goila Butter Chicken Biryani
info.category: Goila Butter Chicken X Biryani by Kilo
info.description:
Introducing Butter Chicken Biryani by GBC X BBK
[Served with Chef’s special Achari Kurkuri boondi and Raita Do Pyaza]
Layers of fragrant, slow-cooked basmati rice with tender pieces of chicken drenched in Chef Saransh Goila’s signature smoky, creamy Makhani Gravy topped with crispy fried onions and crunchy cashews.

info.name: Goila Butter Paneer Biryani

info.description:
Introducing Butter Paneer Biryani by GBC X BBK
[Served with Chef’s special Achari Kurkuri boondi and Raita Do Pyaza]
Layers of fragrant, slow-cooked basmati rice with rich, creamy butter paneer, marinated to perfection in Chef Saransh Goila’s legendary Makhani Gravy, topped with crispy fried onions and crunchy cashews.
